  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Project Manager",
  "description": "<ul><li>1.<strong>Project Planning & Initiation</strong></li><li></li><li><p>Define project scope, objectives, and deliverables.</p></li><li><p>Develop detailed project plans, including timelines, resource allocation, budgets, and risk management strategies.</p></li><li><p>Lead project kickoff meetings to clarify roles, responsibilities, and communication protocols.</p></li><li>2.<strong>Project Execution & Monitoring</strong></li><li></li><li><p>Lead the project team to ensure tasks are executed according to plan.</p></li><li><p>Monitor project progress and track key performance indicators (KPIs).</p></li><li><p>Manage project changes, assess impacts, and update relevant plans.</p></li><li><p>Provide regular status updates to stakeholders.</p></li><li>3.<strong>Resource & Budget Management</strong></li><li></li><li><p>Allocate and manage project resources (human, material, financial).</p></li><li><p>Control project budgets, track expenditures, and ensure costs remain within approved limits.</p></li><li><p>Identify and resolve resource conflicts.</p></li><li>4.<strong>Risk Management & Quality Control</strong></li><li></li><li><p>Identify, assess, and mitigate project risks; develop contingency plans.</p></li><li><p>Ensure project deliverables meet established quality standards and requirements.</p></li><li><p>Conduct quality audits and testing to validate outputs against expectations.</p></li><li>5.<strong>Stakeholder Communication</strong></li><li></li><li><p>Establish and maintain effective communication with clients, suppliers, team members, and senior management.</p></li><li><p>Manage stakeholder expectations and promptly address concerns or conflicts.</p></li><li><p>Organize project review meetings to gather feedback and drive continuous improvement.</p></li><li>6.</li><li><strong>Project Closure & Review</strong></li><li></li><li><p>Ensure projects are completed according to plan and all deliverables are handed over.</p></li><li><p>Facilitate project acceptance and obtain sign-off from clients or sponsors.</p></li><li><p>Prepare project closure reports, archive documentation, and conduct lessons-learned sessions.</p></li></ul>",
